# ============================================================================
# Restaurant Ingredient Tracker - Docker Ignore Configuration
# ============================================================================
#
# This file specifies which files and directories should be excluded from
# the Docker build context to optimize build performance and security.
#
# Benefits:
# - Faster builds by reducing context size
# - Better security by excluding sensitive files
# - Smaller Docker images
# - Reduced network transfer during builds

